										"网络未连接，请检查网络状况", Toast.LENGTH_SHORT)
										.show();
							}
						} else {
							Toast.makeText(FinalMainActivity.this, "请登录账号",
									Toast.LENGTH_SHORT).show();
						}

					}
				});
